'''Kofun Clusters''' (古墳群, ''Kofungun'') are groups of {{ill|kofun|ja|古墳|1=Kofun|12=draft}}—ancient Kofuns—constituting a type of archaeological site.{{Sfn|Nara National Research Institute for Cultural Properties|2020|p=8}}
