== References == * {{Cite book|和書|author=Ōtsuka Hatsushige, Kobayashi Saburō|title=Kofun Jiten|publisher=Tōkyōdō Shuppan|year=1982|date=December 1982|isbn=4-490-10165-1}} * {{Cite book|和書|author=Nara National Research Institute for Cultural Properties|url=https://sitereports.nabunken.go.jp/files/statics/10IsekiJohoKozo.pdf|chapter=The Structure of Archaeological Site Information|title=Simplified Archaeological Site Database|publisher=Nara National Research Institute for Cultural Properties|year=2020|date=2020-06-12|ref=harv}} == See Also == * {{ill|Gunshufun|ja|群集墳|1=Gunshufun|12=draft}} (concentrated kofun clusters) * {{ill|Gaya Tumuli|ja|伽倻古墳群|12=draft}} - A cluster of ancient tombs in Korea, registered as a World Cultural Heritage site in 2023.
